if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b1f63ff36c3f63476ae07c0e95302b610452de","tid":482654,"uid":145233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:24:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88d1b737faea10d8cbe68cb491e3ee2f088579f1","tid":482654,"uid":59538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"如果同和記仲有兩年半約係咪轉台無望呀各位?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885bf910b56e17c4765de523ae5a60cf60d2511a","tid":482654,"uid":51193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果同和記仲有兩年半約係咪轉台無望呀各位?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇望 除非你有特別情況 例如服務完全同份合約係2回事<br />\n 咁就可以去ofca投訴刀仔鋸大樹 睇下佢肯唔肯waive你<br />\n唔得就....祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c14e9b72983194a3ac6067847f7e62fb7f8c100","tid":482654,"uid":156284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09f3c54402b79f2b3af5a3075b230b42d1e2331b","tid":482654,"uid":156284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5ff97649e6f010c934fc3c2b92e0fa9a5d9881e","tid":482654,"uid":156284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7d769c1fd3204cc7561b148a9a491ee438e029c","tid":482654,"uid":146160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"025caa6c618041bcc97c0e91590dec033511e5a4","tid":482654,"uid":61482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f933ab1e9fa4ec27e26454c208968ff77fd363e7